                     </persName>
                  , serjeant in the 48th regiment, to sell and transfer 5,000l. in the three percent consolidated annuities, with intent to defraud the 
                     <persName id="t17960511-27-victim453" type="victimName">
                        <rs id="t17960511-27-viclabel138" type="occupation">Governor and Company of the Bank of England</rs>
